B b = new B(); // A class constructor called,then B class constructor called.
C c = new C(); // A class constructor called,then C class constructor called.
D d = new D(); // A class constructor called,then C class constructor called,then D class constructor called.


8Ô∏è‚É£ Access Control in Inheritance : 
| Modifier  | Child Access             |
| --------- | ------------------------ |
| private   | ‚ùå                        |
| default   | ‚úî (same package)         |
| protected | ‚úî (best for inheritance) |
| public    | ‚úî everywhere             |
Access-control checking Rule:
- is this class accessible?
- if yes, then check access modifier of methods.


9Ô∏è‚É£ HAS-A vs IS-A
        - IS-A ‚Üí Inheritance
        - HAS-A ‚Üí Composition / Aggregation
‚úî Inheritance sirf strict IS-A me use karna chahiye



‚ùå this / super keyword : 
              - Ye object & constructor control ke liye hote hain.
              - Inheritance ka supporting topic hai, core definition nahi.
This keyword Explanation:
it refers instance of current class.
- properties access kr skte ho
- method access kr skte ho
- even static chije v access kr skte ho
- it can't be use inside static area like method,block.
- can call current class constructor like, this(), this(age) etc. but during constructor call it should be the first stament except for method call kbhi v use kr skte ho.
- using this keyword Constructor chaining must be linear, not circular. it can be same class (without inheritance) and with inheritance v hota hai.

Super keyword :
it refers to immediate parent class.
- super.method() aur super.variable Child class ke kisi bhi instance method se call ho sakta hai / Child class ke constructor se bhi call ho sakta hai.
- method ya variable call krte time First statement hona zaroori nahi. agr constructor se kr rhe hai to orna nhi
- Static context (static method / main) se nahi
- can call immediate parent class constructor like, super(), super(age) etc. Parent class constructor ko super() sirf aur sirf child class ke constructor se hi call kiya ja sakta hai.
  and First statement hona mandatory.


‚ùå final keyword :
             - final class / method / variable.
             - Ye inheritance ko restrict karta hai.
             - But inheritance ka definition part nahi.
Final keyword Explanation:
final makes something unchangeable:
- value change is not allowed.
- method override is not allowed.
- class inheritance is not allowed.
